ire a fun place for everyone, certain rules for conduct and behavior inside and outside of roleplaying must be adhered to. Conduct rules, as well as the realms Terms of Service, are the final word in any disagreement. Failure to abide by said rules could result in a ban from Ashenshire.<br>
<br>
You must, at all times, respect your fellow roleplayer. If you have a problem with another member of Ashenshire, please bring it to a support member and they will try to rectify the situation. Any threats or attacks posted in out-of-character boards will be deleted immediately and the poster will be given a warning.<br>
<br>
Swearing, while allowed, is to be kept in check. Swearing out-of-character is never necessary, and is frowned upon, as well as objective material posted in out-of-character forums. Please remember that people from all over the world visit and roleplay here. What you say here may not offend some, but may offend others.<br>
<br>
Offensive and explicit material will not be tolerated within the out-of-character forums. While it is allowed in roleplayed form in in-character forums, explicit material has no place in any other location in Ashenshire.<br>
<br>
Spam is strictly forbidden in the out-of-character forums. Users wishing to advertise for rolepaying related material are allowed to do so, but only in an infrequent manner. Request for affiliation must be directed to a support team member and not be posted in the out-of-character forums. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub98.ezboard.com/bgoergyboysroleplayingpalace.showUserPublicProfile?gid=goergyboy>Goergyboy</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Immortal Sensei</span><br>  Posts: 5<br> <font color=#0000FF>(10/1/03 9:41 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fgoergyboysroleplayingpalacefrm15.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.euroasiasoftware.com/bilder/tiger.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: General Conduct</span><hr size=1> Also try to avoid double posting. Right now it is kind of small so it may be harder to avoid, but please do the best you can. Let's keep this place clean, organized, and spam free. <p>Don't fear that which you do not know I wont hurt you</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub98.ezboard.com/bgoergyboysroleplayingpalace.showUserPublicProfile?gid=clockworkmist>Clockwork Mist</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Fresh Meat</span><br>  Posts: 2<br> <font color=#0000FF>(10/3/03 8:27 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fgoergyboysroleplayingpalacefrm15.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: General Conduct</span><hr size=1> I would also like to add another rule if I may.  <br>
